msgid "gluon-config-mode:welcome"
msgstr ""
"Welcome to the setup wizard of your new Freifunk node. "
"Please fill out the following form and transmit it."

msgid "gluon-config-mode:geoloc-welcome"
msgstr ""
"<p>Welcome to the base setup of your new Freifunk node. "
"On this page we need to know where your node will be located, so that we "
"can select the proper settings for the Freifunk network.</p>"
"<p>If yon want your node to be shown on a map or Freifunk nodes or not "
"can be decided on the next page.</p>"
"<p>Please note that your node needs to be connected to the Internet at this "
"point, to resolve the coordinates to a configuration for that area. Thus, it "
"should be connected (via the yellow ports, if existing) to your internet "
"router (Fritzbox, Speedport or similar).</p>"

msgid "gluon-config-mode:pubkey"
msgstr ""
"This is the public key of your Freifunk node. Please use "
"<a href=\"http://setup.guetersloh.freifunk.net/nodereg.php?key=<%=pubkey%>&hostname=<%=hostname%>&mac=<%=sysconfig.primary_mac%>&coords=<%=location%>\" target=\"_blank\">the pre-filled template</a> "
"to register your node."

msgid "gluon-config-mode:reboot"
msgstr ""
"<p>The node is currently rebooting and will try to connect to other "
"nearby Freifunk nodes  after that. "
"Your can find lots of information on the Freifunk Duckburg community on "
"<a href=\"https://entenhausen.freifunk.net/\">our homepage</a>.</p>"
"<p>To get back to this configuration interface, press the reset button for "
"3 seconds during normal operation. The device will then reboot into config "
"mode.</p>"
"<p>Have fun with your node and exploring the Freifunk network!</p>"
